{"title":"购买贺年卡","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2476","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>好吧，新年到了，要买贺年卡了</p>\n<p>我们知道要买m张贺年卡，且看中n家店铺，每家店铺的存货量和价格不同</p>\n<p>我们最少要花多少钱？</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>包括n+1行</p>\n<p>第一行，m和n</p>\n<p>以下n行，每行两个整数，代表该店铺的贺年卡单价与存货量</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>仅一个整数，表示我们最少要花多少钱</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>10 4</p>\n<p>4 3</p>\n<p>6 2</p>\n<p>8 10</p>\n<p>3 6</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>36</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>样例解释：</p>\n<p>先将最后一家买空（3元*6=18元）</p>\n<p>再将第一家买空（4元*3=12元）</p>\n<p>再从第二家买一张（6元*1=6元）</p>\n<p>刚好十张，总价格36元</p>\n<p>保证结果在长整型以内且总存货量不少于m，保证有且只有一个最优解</p>\n<p>0&lt;m,n&lt;=1000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}